net.sf.mmm.client.ui.api.common

Interface CssStyles


  • public interface CssStyles
    This interface contains the names of common CSS styles.
    NOTE:
    This interface is partially biased. However, we wanted to both have a central definition of the CSS style constants AND a way to provide our internal widgets in a reusable way without a dependency on the UiWidget-API so this is the best compromise done on purpose.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Joerg Hohwiller (hohwille at users.sourceforge.net)
